            'any check is fail-status; warn/info are informational.'
        ),
        epilog=(
            'Examples:\n'
            '  smd diag drop-in psk-recorder\n'
            '  smd diag drop-in your-new-client\n'
            '\n'
            'See docs/ADD-A-CLIENT.md for the full checklist.\n'
        ),
